[SPEAKER_00] u cijelom Rinskom carstvu.

737
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] bio je Židov i nakon tog početnog obrazovanja

738
00:39:52,739 --> 00:39:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] odlazi u Jeruzalem.

739
00:39:54,019 --> 00:39:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon što je primio možda

740
00:39:57,179 --> 00:39:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] najbolju filozofsku podlogu

741
00:39:59,539 --> 00:40:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] koju je mogo u tom trenutku primiti

742
00:40:01,460 --> 00:40:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] odlazi u najbolju školu u Jeruzalemu.

743
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,179
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazi kod Gamalijela

744
00:40:06,179 --> 00:40:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] jednog od najpoznatijih židovskih

745
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] učitelja tog doba.

746
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] I tamo kaže sam Petar

747
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:15,179
[SPEAKER_00] da je odrastao do nogu Gamalijelovih.

748
00:40:15,179 --> 00:40:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] Učio je i upijao sve što je on govorio.

749
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] i učenja koje su se u to vrijeme odvijale

750
00:40:22,699 --> 00:40:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] su najčešće bila u ili oko hrama.

751
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] I on je i za vrijeme tog svog odgoja

752
00:40:28,739 --> 00:40:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] sudjelovao i u svim vjerskim obredima

753
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] i upoznao židovsku tradiciju i kulturu

754
00:40:34,900 --> 00:40:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] u dubinu.

755
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] upoznao je sve pore židovskog društva,

756
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:42,179
[SPEAKER_00] načine razmišljanja, filozofiju,

757
00:40:42,179 --> 00:40:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] njihovo razmišljanje o židovstvu,

758
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] o Bogu, o drugim narodima.

759
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:48,679
[SPEAKER_00] sve je to upoznao.

760
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, kad je završavao svoje obrazovanje,

761
00:40:56,099 --> 00:40:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] pojavila se jedna sekta koja je vjerovala

762
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:03,860
[SPEAKER_00] da je stolar koji je bio raspet na križu židovskih mesija.

763
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:09,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa gore svetom Pavlu u tom trenutku niste mogli reći.

764
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] On je imao klasični židovski mindset.

765
00:41:13,719 --> 00:41:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže da je čak bio, u jednom trenutku je rekao

766
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] da je bio prerevan u praćenju otačkih predaja.

767
00:41:21,059 --> 00:41:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] I njemu je to bilo najveća uvreda koja se je mogla reći.

768
00:41:26,159 --> 00:41:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Taj mesija kojeg je on iščekivo,

769
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] i u tom trenutku se očekivalo da će doći mesija,

770
00:41:32,679 --> 00:41:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] svi su se pripremali, zato nije se znalo kad će,

771
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali su oni mislili da će ta mesija doći

772
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] i osloboditi židove od rimskog ropstva,

773
00:41:41,239 --> 00:41:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] od rimskog pladanja,

774
00:41:43,159 --> 00:41:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] da će postati njihov novi kralj,

775
00:41:45,079 --> 00:41:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] da će obnoviti hram,

776
00:41:46,559 --> 00:41:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] da će obnoviti njihovu snagu koju su oni imali,

777
00:41:49,559 --> 00:41:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti osvojiti sve njihove neprijatelje okolne,

778
00:41:52,420 --> 00:41:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti najjači, najbogatiji.

779
00:41:54,139 --> 00:41:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ovo svjetovno.

780
00:41:56,159 --> 00:41:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dolazi Krist,

781
00:41:58,619 --> 00:42:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji donosi skroz drugu priču,

782
00:42:02,199 --> 00:42:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] skroz drugi pristup,

783
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] umire na križu i on počinje progoniti sve one koji vjeruju u njega.

784
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] I dok u jednom trenutku svog zanosa,

785
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:14,320
[SPEAKER_00] svoje mladosti,

786
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] želi još neke pohapsi,

787
00:42:17,780 --> 00:42:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] dovesti do uhičenja,

788
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] dovesti do kamenovanja,

789
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] kako god već,

790
00:42:20,599 --> 00:42:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] traži od velikog svećenika dopuštenje

791
00:42:23,059 --> 00:42:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ide u Damask

792
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:27,780
[SPEAKER_00] i vrati te učenike nazad.

793
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kristove učenike na sud,

794
00:42:30,519 --> 00:42:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] na šta god bi već tamo se dogodilo s njima.

795
00:42:33,780 --> 00:42:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] I u trenutku on kaže,

796
00:42:36,179 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] oko podneva,

797
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] dok je još jahao tamo,

798
00:42:39,179 --> 00:42:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] svjetlost ga je obasja,

799
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] padne s konja

800
00:42:43,059 --> 00:42:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] i objavio mu se Krist.

801
00:42:47,039 --> 00:42:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] I pita on,

802
00:42:50,139 --> 00:42:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] ko si ti gospodine?

803
00:42:51,340 --> 00:42:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Već tad zna da mu se objavilo nešto što nije očekivao,

804
00:42:55,579 --> 00:42:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što je iza njega.

805
00:42:56,539 --> 00:42:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] Opet koristi taj,

806
00:42:58,880 --> 00:43:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] tu imenicu gospodine,

807
00:43:01,420 --> 00:43:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kirio.

808
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:04,320
[SPEAKER_00] I on mu kaže,

809
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] Savle, Savle, zašto me progoniš?

810
00:43:06,840 --> 00:43:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] I objavio mu se da je on Krist

811
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] i govorimo odi u Damask

812
00:43:11,159 --> 00:43:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] i tu počinje cijela priča o svjetom Pavlu.

813
00:43:13,980 --> 00:43:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je bitno za njegov život,

814
00:43:18,860 --> 00:43:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] da nakon tog obraćenja

815
00:43:20,599 --> 00:43:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] krstio se

816
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] i nije otišao odmah u Jeruzalem

817
00:43:25,659 --> 00:43:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] objavit se svim svojim,

818
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] svojim subraći,

819
00:43:29,880 --> 00:43:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] svim kršćanima, židovima,

820
00:43:31,940 --> 00:43:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego je vjerojatno zbog toga što je bio potresen,

821
00:43:36,039 --> 00:43:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] duboko potresen onim što mu se dovodilo,

822
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] njegov cijeli život se okrenuo na opačke,

823
00:43:41,159 --> 00:43:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] on odlučio otići u Arabiji u pustinju

824
00:43:43,219 --> 00:43:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] na tri godine.

825
00:43:43,900 --> 00:43:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tri godine nije ništa radio,

826
00:43:46,599 --> 00:43:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali je tri godine proveo molitvi

827
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] s Kristom.

828
00:43:51,239 --> 00:43:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] I samo možemo nagađati što se tamo događalo,

829
00:43:54,460 --> 00:43:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono što se dogodilo je da se

830
00:43:57,260 --> 00:43:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao,

831
00:43:58,219 --> 00:43:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dotad

832
00:43:59,659 --> 00:44:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] revnovao

833
00:44:01,820 --> 00:44:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] za otačke predaje,

834
00:44:03,320 --> 00:44:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] ubijao kršćane,

835
00:44:05,159 --> 00:44:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] progonio ih,

836
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] vratio i postao

837
00:44:07,679 --> 00:44:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] najveći evangelizator.

838
00:44:09,739 --> 00:44:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što se tamo dogodilo

839
00:44:13,440 --> 00:44:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] je moralo promijeniti njegovo srce,

840
00:44:15,920 --> 00:44:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] koje je već bilo jako dotaknuto

841
00:44:18,840 --> 00:44:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] onim trenutkom obraćenja,

842
00:44:21,219 --> 00:44:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali je moralo promijeniti njegov um.

843
00:44:25,380 --> 00:44:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao, koji se vratio,

844
00:44:27,099 --> 00:44:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] više nije razmišljao

845
00:44:30,139 --> 00:44:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] u Izraelu na način na koji je razmišljava,

846
00:44:32,159 --> 00:44:35,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego je shvatio

847
00:44:35,039 --> 00:44:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] koja je Kristova poruka.

848
00:44:36,659 --> 00:44:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] Shvatio je

849
00:44:38,300 --> 00:44:39,719
[SPEAKER_00] sva ona obećanja

850
00:44:39,719 --> 00:44:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja je na pamet znao.

851
00:44:41,460 --> 00:44:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] Toru, Talmud,

852
00:44:44,099 --> 00:44:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve ono što je obećano

853
00:44:45,460 --> 00:44:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] i što su proroci rekli

854
00:44:46,619 --> 00:44:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] o tome kako će Mesija izgledat,

855
00:44:48,980 --> 00:44:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] shvatio je na pravi i stvaran način

856
00:44:51,599 --> 00:44:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] i shvatio je da se to dogodilo u Kristu.

857
00:44:53,860 --> 00:44:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zato mu je trebalo tri pune godine.

858
00:44:55,820 --> 00:44:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] Da mu je trebalo mjesec dana,

859
00:44:58,360 --> 00:45:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno bi Isus to mjesec dana napravio.

860
00:45:00,500 --> 00:45:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bez obzira što je to bilo

861
00:45:02,280 --> 00:45:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] toliko snažno iskustvo,

862
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] njemu je trebalo tri godine

863
00:45:04,519 --> 00:45:07,320
[SPEAKER_00] da se njegov um preobrazi,

864
00:45:07,320 --> 00:45:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] njegovo srce preobrazi,

865
00:45:08,980 --> 00:45:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mogo biti ono što je postao kasnije.

866
00:45:11,599 --> 00:45:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] I tu i mi sami sebi moramo dat

867
00:45:15,599 --> 00:45:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno vremena

868
00:45:17,519 --> 00:45:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] i dovoljno kredita

869
00:45:18,840 --> 00:45:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] da kad se obratimo,

870
00:45:20,019 --> 00:45:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] da pustimo Bogu

871
00:45:21,699 --> 00:45:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] da odradi ono što On treba odraditi u nama.

872
00:45:23,860 --> 00:45:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ne bi puno više ulazio

873
00:45:27,239 --> 00:45:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] u opise Petra koji su iz knjiga,

874
00:45:30,360 --> 00:45:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] nego bi htio vas uvest

875
00:45:33,199 --> 00:45:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] u ovu njegovu zlatnu nit

876
00:45:36,260 --> 00:45:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] o koju sam već spomenuo,

877
00:45:37,840 --> 00:45:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] to je da je bio poučen

878
00:45:39,699 --> 00:45:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] u grškoj kulturi,

879
00:45:40,860 --> 00:45:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] poznavao je kulturu Rimskog carstva

880
00:45:43,119 --> 00:45:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] jako dobro,

881
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:47,179
[SPEAKER_00] odgojen je do noguga Malijelovih,

882
00:45:47,179 --> 00:45:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] znači upoznao je židove jako dobro

883
00:45:49,300 --> 00:45:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] i ono treće što ga je krasilo

884
00:45:51,579 --> 00:45:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] je to da je bio rimski građanin.

885
00:45:53,739 --> 00:45:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

886
00:45:55,179 --> 00:45:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao je u sebi spojio

887
00:45:57,179 --> 00:45:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] tri nespojive stvari.

888
00:45:59,099 --> 00:46:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] Boga je tako vodio

889
00:46:01,900 --> 00:46:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] da je on upoznao

890
00:46:03,320 --> 00:46:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli onaj sustav

891
00:46:04,920 --> 00:46:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji je u tom vremenu djelovao

892
00:46:06,539 --> 00:46:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] od kulturnog helenizma

893
00:46:09,059 --> 00:46:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio pokorio tadi Rim

894
00:46:10,579 --> 00:46:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] do uprave rimske

895
00:46:12,699 --> 00:46:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja je tamo bila

896
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] koju je upoznavao do kraja

897
00:46:14,739 --> 00:46:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjet ćemo da je poznao

898
00:46:15,739 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] rimsko građansko pravo

899
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] koje je studirao pravo u Zagrebu

900
00:46:18,940 --> 00:46:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] i poznao je židove.

901
00:46:22,099 --> 00:46:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] Poznao je ih iznutra,

902
00:46:23,699 --> 00:46:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] poznao je njihov mindset,

903
00:46:25,059 --> 00:46:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] poznao je njihove načine

904
00:46:27,980 --> 00:46:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] na koji su djelovali,

905
00:46:29,159 --> 00:46:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] njihove obrede,

906
00:46:30,079 --> 00:46:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] njihove zakone.

907
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je poznao.

908
00:46:32,840 --> 00:46:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko je duboko ušao

909
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] od svaki od tih sustava,

910
00:46:35,900 --> 00:46:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] Boga je toliko duboko uveo,

911
00:46:38,320 --> 00:46:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] bio je toliko revan

912
00:46:39,599 --> 00:46:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] da je sve valjda istraživo

913
00:46:41,300 --> 00:46:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] i da je sve upio.

914
00:46:42,139 --> 00:46:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jer atno ste upoznali one ljude

915
00:46:44,079 --> 00:46:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] čim se nećim počnu baviti

916
00:46:45,780 --> 00:46:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] odmah uđu toliko srce muto

917
00:46:47,559 --> 00:46:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] da sve skuže,

918
00:46:49,159 --> 00:46:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] da ih sve zanima,

919
00:46:50,760 --> 00:46:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] samo kopaju, kopaju, kopaju.

920
00:46:52,380 --> 00:46:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] I onda doživljava obraćenje,

921
00:46:55,460 --> 00:46:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] kriz ga izvodi u pustinju,

922
00:46:57,659 --> 00:46:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] prooblikuje ga,

923
00:46:59,119 --> 00:47:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] proobražava ga,

924
00:47:00,039 --> 00:47:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] spaja ga sa samim sobom,

925
00:47:01,559 --> 00:47:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] daje mu ono što je on imao,

926
00:47:04,480 --> 00:47:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] daje mu ljubav

927
00:47:05,360 --> 00:47:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ga šalje nazad.

928
00:47:06,820 --> 00:47:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] Šalje da počne rovariti

929
00:47:08,980 --> 00:47:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] u tim sustavima,

930
00:47:10,079 --> 00:47:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] da počinje donosi samo Krista

931
00:47:12,159 --> 00:47:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] u te sustave.

932
00:47:14,840 --> 00:47:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ono što ćemo sad proći

933
00:47:18,599 --> 00:47:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] je jedan mali prisik

934
00:47:19,860 --> 00:47:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] događaja koje donose dijela apostolska.

935
00:47:24,480 --> 00:47:27,900
